<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="csrf-token" content="<%= csrfToken %>" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="./css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Sports Scheduler</title>
    <style>
        section {
            display: flex;
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .h1 {
            font-family: brush script mt, cursive;
            color: rgba(87, 2, 167, 0.77);
            font-size: 5.5vw;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .h2 {
            font-family: lucida handwriting, cursive;
            color: rgb(246, 245, 241);
            font-size: 3.0vw;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .h3 {
            font-size: lucida handwriting, cursive;
            color: rgb(253, 253, 255);
            font-size: 2.0vw;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .split {
            height: 100%;
            width: 50%;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: 1;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .left {
            left: 0;
        }

        .right {
            right: 0;
        }

        .para {
            font-family: arrial;
            color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
            font-size: 2.0vw;
        }

        .centered {
            position: absolute;
            top: 60%;
            left: 30%;
            transform: translate(-30%, -50%);
            text-align: center;
        }

        #home {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)),
                url("./main.jpg");
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            flex-direction: column;

        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <section id="home">
        <h1 class="h1">
            Sports Scheduler
        </h1>
        <h2 class="h2">Welcome to the Sports Scheduler</h2><br><br>
        <div class="split left">
            <div class="centered">
                <p class="para">This website pages a crucial role in simplifying the process of creating and managing
                    the
                    sports, where players can join sport and schedule their sessions.
                    Moreover, helping to maintain the integrety and excitment in sports.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="split right">
            <div class="centered">
                <h3 class="para">New here? <a href="/Signup_Page" style="color:rgb(247, 152, 9)">Sign-up now</a></h3>
                <h3 class="para">Already have an account? <a href="/Login_Page"
                        style="color:rgb(248, 163, 6)">Sign-in</a></h3>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>

</html>
